It is used for storing data and playing with database.
Data is store in form of docuemnts.
It uses BSON to query database.(internally and over the network)(in a JSON like format)
Storing data is called collection.
BSON stores data in Binary representation. It is also known as binary json.
Json is used for transmission but Bson is used for stroing data.
MongoDB is a schema-less NoSQL document database.

Mongoose is a npm package and manages relationship between data provide schema validation. It is an Object Data Modeling(ODM) library for MongoDB and Node.js.
It provides abstraction data layer on MongoDB.